    "body": "Probably a result of https://github.com/pydata/pandas/issues/12363 fixing groupby sometimes losing the name.\n\nIn this case I'd say that\n\n``` python\nIn [37]: df.groupby('a').b.value_counts().reset_index(name='counts')\nOut[37]:\n   a  b  counts\n0  0  1       2\n1  0  2       1\n2  1  1       1\n```\n\nis even clearer than your original. Thoughts?\n"
